Instructions for starting an ISO42001-compliant FHIR project with provenance

1. Copy bootstrap-cowork.sh from github

2. Change permissions chmod u+x bootstrap-cowork.sh

3. Run ./bootstrap-cowork.sh from within the directory where you will create and edit the FHIR files

4. Run "./audit/log_action.sh "Initiating new AI development session for project sushi""

5. Run "./provenance/create_provenance.sh"

6. Run claude #from hereon, all changes are recorded using ISO42001-compliant guidelines



